text: The Courthouse of Lillehammer Sør-Gudbrandsdal District Court (Norwegian: Sør- Gudbrandsdal tingrett) is a district court located in Lillehammer, Norway. It covers the municipalities of Lillehammer, Gausdal, Øyer, Ringebu and Sør-Fron and is subordinate to the Eidsivating Court of Appeal.
